author: Reuters
title: BRIEF-Groupe Open Q3 revenue up 5 pct at 65.3 million euros
text:
Oct 22 Groupe Open SA :
* Confirms FY revenue outlook about 280 million euros ($311.44 million)
* Q3 revenue 65.3 million euros versus 62.3 million euros year ago
* Confirms expected FY operating income and net income in significant growth
